node.text: Amber Ruffin does some of my favorite bits of Late Night with Seth Meyers. I don’t know her (I met her once, which was exciting, because I love her) but what a goddamn generous act, to be willing to share these stories about such traumatizing experiences, especially after being repeatedly told to “take it in stride.” @amberruffin

node.text:
I’m pleased to announce that during quarantine I grew ten inches and am now officially A Tall™️. (It’s not the camera angle or the shoes. I will not be taking questions.) 
Sincerely, A Tall.

node.text: I put on heels for the first time in a year! I went somewhere! I was super awkward with everyone I interacted with! But hey, I won a Kids Choice Award! Thanks KIDS 💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫

node.text: Amber Ruffin does some of my favorite bits of Late Night with Seth Meyers. I don’t know her (I met her once, which was exciting, because I love her) but what a goddamn generous act, to be willing to share these stories about such traumatizing experiences, especially after being repeatedly told to “take it in stride.” @amberruffin
